ONE廠牌行動電話壹支（SIM卡壹張，號碼：0000000000，IMEI：000000000000000）沒收。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/SLDM/111%2c%e8%a8%b4%2c33%2c20220803%2c3/pdf"},"JID":"SLDM,111,訴,33,20220803,3","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"訴","JNO":"33","JDATE":"20220803","JTITLE":"毒品危害防制條例等"}